WEBVTT

00:04.440 --> 00:06.120
Do them again, and do them better.

00:06.160 --> 00:08.160
Our little family,
all together again.

00:08.200 --> 00:11.120
Well, come on then!
Stop it! Stop it!

00:11.560 --> 00:14.440
Tony, you're a disgrace!

00:14.480 --> 00:16.600
I know, I know, don't be a bore.

00:16.640 --> 00:18.640
That's young Tony Travers,
he's her lover.

00:18.680 --> 00:20.360
I'm Roderick Temple. I'm a painter.

00:21.320 --> 00:23.040
I'm a married woman.

00:23.080 --> 00:25.760
The Spirit of Selfridges
is quite the thing.

00:25.800 --> 00:28.880
Doesn't she look ravishing? Your
husband seems to think so anyway.

00:30.960 --> 00:34.080
♪ You are my honey honeysuckle

00:34.120 --> 00:37.680
♪ You are the bee

00:37.720 --> 00:41.640
♪ I like to sip the honey sweet

00:41.680 --> 00:44.800
♪ From those red lips you see

00:44.920 --> 00:48.720
♪ I love you dearly dearly

00:48.760 --> 00:52.000
♪ And I want you to love me...

00:53.120 --> 00:56.800
♪ You are my honey...

00:56.840 --> 00:59.800
♪ I am the bee...

01:07.960 --> 01:09.760
I love watching you make up.

01:09.800 --> 01:13.280
Although you don't need it.
You look beautiful without.

01:13.320 --> 01:16.640
I'm a showgirl.
It's what people expect.

01:16.680 --> 01:19.400
Hm. How old were you
when you got your first break?

01:19.440 --> 01:21.520
Eighteen.

01:21.560 --> 01:24.640
The leading lady fell ill, and they
pulled me from the Chorus Line.

01:24.680 --> 01:29.040
I was still Joyce then.
Joyce Humphries.

01:29.080 --> 01:30.840
Really?

01:30.880 --> 01:36.720
The director said, "Your dancing's
good, but your name is rotten."

01:36.760 --> 01:39.440
He gave me an hour to come up
with a new one. Ah.

01:41.280 --> 01:44.640
♪ I love you dearly dearly

01:44.680 --> 01:47.920
♪ And I want you to love me

01:49.680 --> 01:52.240
Harry, I can't.

01:52.280 --> 01:54.560
I can't, I haven't got time,
and neither have you -

01:54.600 --> 01:57.640
I always have time!

